name: RGSS1-scripts
body:
# RGSS1-Scripts
RGSS1(RMXP) scripts for RM users. Most of them serve as plugin scripts in RPG Maker XP.
## Contents
* 66RPG RMXP library backup
* Self-made plugins

You don't need to report when using these scripts.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
